\c 20
\s VaAsiriya vachakunda Egipita neItiyopiya
\p
\v 1 Negore rekusvika kwaTaritani paAshidhodhi, Sarigoni mambo weAsiriya paakamutuma, akarwa neAshidhodhi ndokuritapa;
\v 2 panguva iyo Jehovha wakataura neruoko rwaIsaya mwanakomana waAmozi, achiti: Enda, unosunungura saga kubva pazviuno zvako, ubvise nyatera rako kubva parutsoka rwako. Zvino wakaita saizvozvo zchifamba akashama uye asina manyatera.
\v 3 Zvino Jehovha wakati: Muranda wangu Isaya sezvaakafamba akashama uye asina manyatera makore matatu, chiratidzo nechishamiso kuEgipita nekunItiyopiya;
\v 4 saizvozvo mambo weAsiriya achatinha vatapwa veEgipita nevakadzingwa veItiyopiya, vadiki nevakuru, Vakashama, vasina manyatera, magadziko ari pachena, chive chinyadzo cheEgipita.
\v 5 Zvino vachavhunduka vakanyara pamusoro peItiyopiya, chivimbo chavo, neEgipita rumbidzo yavo.
\v 6 Zvino mugari wechitsuwa vachati nezuva iro: Tarirai, chakadaro chivimbo chedu, chatichatizira rubatsiro kuti tisunungurwe pachiso chamambo weAsiriya; Zvino isu tichapukunyuka sei?
